text: Some of the charts need work though - the source conversion effectiveness one needs normalisation to account for differing traffic levels. Usually though this sort of “a bit of everything” dashboard helps us identify the real question, then we focus content on answering just that

It’s a high-level summary of some useful digital metrics and KPIs, and the starting point to investigate some that look significant or interesting. For example - I’m ranking much lower than expected for key search keywords than I’d expected, why is this, etc
What business decisions did this data viz lead to?
